secondary_street_name: lying adjacent to the Moorgate Line
description: Redesign of the Drayton Park development as approved under ref. P011500 on 30 May 2002 and ref. P032699 on 23 December 2003 in order to provide 278 housing units and a Community Health Facility with associated areas of car parking and landscaping.
decision_conditions:
CONDITION:  None of the parking spaces hereby approved shall be used for any other purpose than for parking motor vehicles and no trade or business shall be operated from any of the approved spaces without the prior written approval of the Local Planning Authority.

REASON:  In order to safeguard the amenities of nearby residential occupiers.
